profile: Stephanie entered the interior design field in 2015, but her love for design far outdates that. Her first job at a home décor boutique sparked her passion for design and decorating. Along with her custom millwork industry experience she has an education in business, interior decorating, kitchen and bath standards and interior design. Stephanie’s ambition to educate herself on kitchen and bath standards and practices as well as interior design trends is endless. She looks forward to applying this inspiration and knowledge to your upcoming project.
